4. Orchestration & CI/CD  
   - Define Airflow DAGs; add unit tests for transformations; use GitOps for deployments.  
5. Monitoring & Observability  
   - Collect metrics (Prometheus), logs (ELK/Opensearch), and tracing (Jaeger). Add alerting for lag, throughput, and job failures.  
6. Security & Governance  
   - Enable encryption at rest/in transit, RBAC, schema registry, and data lineage tools.

